## Site frequency spectrum ##

[] I have .saf files

    [+] 

        # realSFS $outFolder/angsdput.saf.idx 

        [] do SFS with chromosome or region => add -r $region
            region can be in 22 or 22:1000000-150000000000 format

        [] limit to a fixed number of sites => add -nSites $sites
 

    [-] 

do you have the gl files

        Generate .saf files

        # angsd -infileType $infileName -ref $ref -GL $gl -anc $anc -dosaf $doSaf -out $outFolder
        
        [] Do filtering => add filters: 
            
            -baq $baq 
            -C $C 
            -minMapQ $minMapQ 
            -minQ $minQ 
                
                # realSFS $outFolder/angsdput.saf.idx 

                [] do SFS with chromosome or region => add -r $region
                   (region can be in 22 or 22:1000000-150000000000 format)

                [] limit to a fixed number of sites => add -nSites $sites
